Escape to your own slice of paradise with this charming villa nestled along the peaceful Kampot river. Just a short 12-minute drive from Durian Roundabout, this property offers a perfect blend of convenience and tranquility.
Spread across a spacious 5,106 square meters of land, the villa boasts stunning river views and plenty of space to unwind. With six cozy bedrooms, each with its own bathroom, there's plenty of room for family and friends to relax.
Inside, you'll find comfy living areas perfect for gathering and a large kitchen for cooking up delicious meals. There are also separate guest units for privacy or hosting visitors.

And with double glazed windows for added security and peace and quiet, you can truly relax and enjoy your riverside retreat.
Come experience the simple luxury of waterfront living in Kampotâ€”this villa is waiting for you to call it home.
